Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hawk-Eye Mihawk! The Great\NSwordsman Zoro Falls on the Sea"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ugh...\N--What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami ran off with the Going Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Big Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're impressive as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've set your eyes\Non a big bounty pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Arlong is the one pirate\Nthat you shouldn't go after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's super terrifyingly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept himself quiet\Nand out of sight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he started going\Nwild again recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's hard to give up on that\N20-million berry bounty, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's so strong that\Nthere's a shred of possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even we may be killed by a hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, I'm sorry, but could you\Nturn around? I want to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change? Here? Now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True to her looks, she's so bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt if we take\Na quick peek, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? Of course, business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thief that only targets\Npirates. I'll take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that I became a member.\NI just joined forces with them. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only spent a short time with Luffy\Nand the others, but I had lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tell them...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that if we're linked\Nby fate, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! We'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were more or less\Nasked to watch the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how she took the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She's making\Nthis crisis worse for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya gave that ship to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I can still see it!\NIt's the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Leave right away!\NTake that ship and follow Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.\NJust give that ship to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need of going after that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept anyone\Nbut her as our navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right...\NWhat a high-maintenance captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Usopp, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro Zoro, the ship is ready!\N--Big Bro Zoro, the ship is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go since I haven't settled\Nanything at this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.\NThe situation here isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What the hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's been split into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the man who destroyed our fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He followed us here... to kill us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's strongest man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man who sank Krieg's\N50 ships on his own in the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the one who destroyed\NKrieg's ship just now is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he looks just like\Nan ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like he\Nhas any special weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weapon is on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really slice up that large\Nsailing ship using that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the master swordsman Hawk-Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man who stands above all\Nother swordsmen in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd be\Nable to see him this soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally... time to fulfill my promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What grudge do you\Nhave to come after us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Don't mock us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I aimed straight for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He averted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gently changed\Nthe course of the bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the point of his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three swords... Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a sword\Nmoved so gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no strength in\Nswordplay based only on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use that sword to\Nslice up this ship as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came out to sea to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph... How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got spare time,\Nright? Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This guy is Zoro! Roronoa Zoro\Nof the Three Swords Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a pirate hunter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't good, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry will\Nbe out of sight soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? Hmph! How pitiful, weak one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are a competent\Nenough swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to see\Nthe disparity in our abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even before we cross swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your courage or ignorance that\Ncauses you to turn your sword on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also because of a\Npromise I made to a dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk,\Nthe world's strongest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the pirate hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fight will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can't possibly be anyone\Nwho can defeat Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro is the strongest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the meaning of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no beast that goes all\Nout when hunting a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're a swordsman who's\Nearned a bit of a name for himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this sea, the East Blue, is the\Nweakest among the four seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't carry any\Nsmaller sharp instrument than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not regret it when I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frog in the well...\NKnow how big the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni... Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Big Bro's Oni Giri was stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a big technique that never\Nfails to blow any enemy away was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't move them! What did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever seen\Nthrough this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he stopped it using a toy like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our abilities are this far apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right!\NThere's no way that it's this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's strongest can't be this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening,\Nright, Big Bro?! Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be this far apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ferocity your swordplay has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking Zoro's Three Swords Style\Nattacks with such a small knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster even beyond\Nthe monstrous Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pursue\Nswordsmanship all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be dealt with by a toy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... If only I had been born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be whining like\Nthat after you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair! You're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, one of us will be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a promise!\N--It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become the world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm going to get\Nstronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the world's greatest swordsman\Nso that my name will reach heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only to defeat this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you bear on your shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you desire once you've\Nobtained power, weak one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called Big Bro a\Nweak one? You cross bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you a lesson! He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Yosaku! Johnny!\NDon't intervene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!\NThe world's greatest swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would need\Nno less than that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to\Nlet me pierce your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I withdrew even a step,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like those various\Nimportant things such as pledges
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and promises in the\Npast will be shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won't be able to come\Nback to where I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what defeat is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all the more reason\NI can't withdraw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strong heart!\NSo he chooses death over defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen anyone like you\Nin a while, strong one. Thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a swordsman's courtesy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sink you using the world's\Nstrongest black sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He took it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sword that sliced up the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this'll be the last hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be the world's strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! That's enough! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Swords Style Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I'd ever lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power\Nof the world's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars on the back are\Na swordsman's shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't live so hastily, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!!\N--Big Bro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I decided to become\Nthe strongest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to devote my life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy! His opponent\Nis the real world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How it'd turn out was clear. He should\Ngive up his ambition rather than die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy...\Nto give up your ambition, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of the Grand Line...\Nthe power of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the pirate hunter Zoro\Nis as helpless as a new-born baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, damn you... Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!!\N--Big Bro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that brat... has the\Npower of a devil fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that young\Nswordsman's comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also impressed me for\Nwatching it to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I didn't kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry up and get\Nhim up on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is medicine! Throw it over him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for you to die.\NMy name is Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn about yourself!\NLearn about the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold this seat of\Nthe strongest and wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to surpass me! Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he got Hawk-Eye\NMihawk to say this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, what is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even harder than surpassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know when\NI haven't done it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!\N--Big Bro! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need no less than the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Please don't talk any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I will not be defeated ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day I defeat him\Nand become a master swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never... be defeated!\NGot any problems with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good team.\NI want to see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to take my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the life of the East\NBlue's ruler, Don Krieg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to, but I had enough fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going home to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have had enough,\Nbut I'm tired of getting beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to keep him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die before you leave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected...\Nhe never learns a lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! I'll leave Nami to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Zoro and I will\Nbring Nami back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get that cook to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all five of us\Nare reunited, let's go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We ran into some interference,\Nbut the real fight starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, can I stop doing\Nchores if I drive them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Krieg and his pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what an\Nungrateful bunch they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.71,0:24:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they were given food!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's another ungrateful one\Nwho took treasure and ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't worry\Nabout it! Get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a weird guy came out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fully armed with shields!\NOw, ow, ow! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.99,0:24:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadly Foot Technique Bursts Forth!\NSanji vs. the Invincible Pearl"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.66,0:24:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
